title: Ebro In The Morning - Serena Williams Retirement + White-Ish Wednesday
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/10/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about Trump's Mar-a-Lago home being raided by the FBI, Skete Davidson, Kanye, and Kim's love triangle, Serena Williams retirement and more!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
